While MC usually enjoys Prolific studies it has to be said that this one was average. It was just really repetitive. Also it was a huge mental effort, it was possible to learn one set, but the others were just impossible especially when the cat went back and forwards. Also there was no incentive to make a massive effort to learn all the colours because it was always a 6p bonus payment if one was quick. Seriously there was no difference between getting 17% and 83% which was just weird. Also it's a shame that there's not a proper text box because if there was MC would post his donation spiel. It's been posted on pretty much every other survey site and MC wants to knock this place off the list as well. Finally it has to be said that the town was really nice.
